{
  "stem": "3474.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's how we used to know something what's going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But otherwise you lost, you lost track of time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't even know what the-- You know, I was in the camp only about a little over a year.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it seems to me like I was there for 20 years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And now it's what do you-- like, I tell you now, and you come back tomorrow, could tell you different stories, so many difference, different.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Flashbacks come back to me so bad that I just-- different ones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The same-- what I, what I went through, the same stories, different stories, but I can't tell you exactly now exactly everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I could tell you so many different stories from marching and from the camp alone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was just-- you know, you, you wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't even believe it that I could, could do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, it bo-- people, the people I was working with, they could have helped us a little bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they, they were afraid, probably.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The civilians were afraid, probably.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the Nazis, the Germans, they wouldn't help us at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They just used to chase, chase, chase [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's all they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were-- and they-- not on top of that, they didn't give us anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They used to sit down, lunch time, take out the food and sit down and eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were just watching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We couldn't eat nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and we were there till about March, Ap-April.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From April, we were starting to march from over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, they put us in cattle train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "April-- was still snow over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put us in cattle train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The snow was still in the-- in the trains.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
